<lb n="0783c12" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"></cb:mulu><note n="0783004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】康安元年寫東寺金剛藏本，【甲】正德二年栂尾本寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】青蓮院藏本，上卷長久五年寫，下卷安元三年寫，【丙】鎌倉初期寫東寺金剛藏本</note><cb:jhead>兩部大法相承師資付法記上</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0783c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0783c14" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="author">兩部付法次第記海雲記</byline>
<lb n="0783c15" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><p xml:id="pT51p0783c1501">略敘金剛界大教王<note n="0783005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經〕－【甲】</note><note n="0783005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0783005"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>師資相承<note n="0783006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">付＝傳【甲】</note><note n="0783006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">付【大】，傳【甲】</note><app n="0783006"><lem wit="【大】">付</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">傳</rdg></app>法次第
<lb n="0783c16" ed="T"/>記。</p>
<lb n="0783c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT51p0783c1701">三藏金剛智云。我從<note n="0783007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">南＋（天）【甲】</note><note n="0783007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">南【大】，南天【甲】</note><app n="0783007"><lem wit="【大】">南</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南天</rdg></app>竺國。親於龍智阿闍
<lb n="0783c18" ed="T"/>梨邊。傳得此金剛界百千頌經。<note n="0783008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔龍智〕－【甲】</note><note n="0783008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">龍智【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0783008"><lem wit="【大】">龍智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>阿闍
<lb n="0783c19" ed="T"/>梨自云。從毘盧遮那如來<note place="inline">即釋迦如來是此<note n="0783009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">約＝旦ィ【甲】</note><note n="0783009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">約【大】，旦【校異-甲】</note><app n="0783009"><lem wit="【大】">約</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">旦</rdg></app>法性身為名</note>在
<lb n="0783c20" ed="T"/>世。以此金剛界最上乘法。付<note n="0783010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">屬＝囑【甲】</note><note n="0783010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">屬【大】，囑【甲】</note><app n="0783010"><lem wit="【大】">屬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囑</rdg></app>普賢金剛薩
<lb n="0783c21" ed="T"/>埵。普賢金剛薩埵<note n="0783011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（付妙…代））十六字＝（（經數百年））四字【甲】</note><note n="0783011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（付妙…代）十六字【大】，經數百年【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="16" n="0783011"><lem wit="【大】">付妙吉祥菩薩。妙吉祥菩
<lb n="0783c22" ed="T"/>薩<note n="0783012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">復＝後【乙】＊</note><note n="0783012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】＊，後【乙】＊</note><app n="0783012"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">後</rdg></app>經十二代</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">經數百年</rdg></app>。以法付囑龍猛菩薩<note place="inline">龍猛<note n="0783013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔菩薩〕－【甲】</note><note n="0783013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菩薩【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0783013"><lem wit="【大】">菩薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>即龍
<lb n="0783c23" ed="T"/>樹菩薩也。菩薩生時於龍樹下生故名龍樹也</note>龍猛菩薩又經數百年以
<lb n="0783c24" ed="T"/>法付囑龍智阿闍梨。龍智阿闍梨又經<note n="0783014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">百餘＝數百【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0783014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">百餘【大】，數百【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0783014"><lem wit="【大】">百餘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】">數百</rdg></app>
<lb n="0783c25" ed="T"/>年<note place="inline">此二聖者道果成就。皆壽數百歲</note><note n="0783015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝又以此【甲】</note><note n="0783015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，又以此【甲】</note><app n="0783015"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">又以此</rdg></app>法<note n="0783016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">付＋（囑）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0783016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">付【大】，付囑【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0783016"><lem wit="【大】">付</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】">付囑</rdg></app>金剛智三<note n="0783017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">藏＋（阿闍梨）【甲】</note><note n="0783017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏【大】，藏阿闍梨【甲】</note><app n="0783017"><lem wit="【大】">藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">藏阿闍梨</rdg></app><note place="inline">梵云
<lb n="0783c26" ed="T"/><note n="0783018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囀＝縛【甲】</note><note n="0783018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囀【大】，縛【甲】</note><app n="0783018"><lem wit="【大】">囀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>曰羅（二合）吉孃（二合）<note n="0783019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曩＝那【甲】</note><note n="0783019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曩【大】，那【甲】</note><app n="0783019"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">那</rdg></app>此云金剛智</note><note n="0783020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔金剛智〕－【甲】</note><note n="0783020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">金剛智【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0783020"><lem wit="【大】">金剛智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三藏和<note n="0783021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尚＝上【甲】＊</note><note n="0783021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尚【大】＊，上【甲】＊</note><app n="0783021"><lem wit="【大】">尚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">上</rdg></app>蘊
<lb n="0783c27" ed="T"/>大小乘。宗一切有部。住戒霜潔。律為提塘。南
<lb n="0783c28" ed="T"/>天竺國王第三子為弘法故杖錫五天。來遊
<lb n="0783c29" ed="T"/>震旦。時有中天竺國三藏。性釋迦氏。斛飯
<pb n="0784a" xml:id="T51.2081.0784a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0784a01" ed="T"/>王五十二代孫因父王使<note n="0784001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">命＝令【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0784001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命【大】，令【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0784001"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】">令</rdg></app>征戰。遂見殺戮
<lb n="0784a02" ed="T"/>殘害者眾。遂不樂王位。厭世出家。誓願傳
<lb n="0784a03" ed="T"/>法東國。與金剛智三藏。於玄宗朝同為國師
<lb n="0784a04" ed="T"/>知三藏金藏智解金剛界法。遂於金剛智三
<lb n="0784a05" ed="T"/>藏請傳金剛界五部法。時三藏金剛智知中
<lb n="0784a06" ed="T"/>天竺國無畏三藏解大毘盧遮那教。歎言此
<lb n="0784a07" ed="T"/>法甚深<note n="0784002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔難逢〕ィ－【甲】</note><note n="0784002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">難逢【大】，〔－〕【校異-甲】</note><app n="0784002"><lem wit="【大】">難逢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>難遇昔於南天竺國聞有大毘
<lb n="0784a08" ed="T"/>盧遮那<note n="0784003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">教＝胎藏【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0784003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教【大】，胎藏【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0784003"><lem wit="【大】">教</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【丙】">胎藏</rdg></app>名。遂遊五天訪求都無解者。今
<lb n="0784a09" ed="T"/>至大唐喜遇此<note n="0784004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">教＝法【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0784004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教【大】，法【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0784004"><lem wit="【大】">教</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】">法</rdg></app>。遂請無畏三藏求授大毘
<lb n="0784a10" ed="T"/>盧遮那大教。亘為師資傳授二<note n="0784005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">本＋（大）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0784005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本【大】，本大【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0784005"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】">本大</rdg></app>教。三藏金
<lb n="0784a11" ed="T"/>剛智阿闍梨又將此金剛界大教王付大興善
<lb n="0784a12" ed="T"/>寺三藏不空智阿闍梨。三藏<note n="0784006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔不空智〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不空智【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784006"><lem wit="【大】">不空智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>和<app type="star" corresp="#0783021"><lem wit="【大】">尚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">上</rdg></app>
<lb n="0784a13" ed="T"/>又以<note n="0784007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔此〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784007"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0784008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＋（傳）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0784008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，法傳【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0784008"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】">法傳</rdg></app>付<note n="0784009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囑＝保壽寺【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0784009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囑【大】，保壽寺【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0784009"><lem wit="【大】">囑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】">保壽寺</rdg></app>含光<note n="0784010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔阿闍梨〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0784010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿闍梨【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0784010"><lem wit="【大】">阿闍梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>等弟子五
<lb n="0784a14" ed="T"/>人。一含光<app type="star" corresp="#0784010"><lem wit="【大】">阿闍梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note place="inline">代宗皇帝<note n="0784011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784011"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>勅令修北五臺山<note n="0784012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔造〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">造【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784012"><lem wit="【大】">造</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>金閣寺不暇傳法</note>二
<lb n="0784a15" ed="T"/>大興善寺惠朗阿闍梨<note place="inline">傳於崇福寺天竺阿闍梨天竺阿闍梨傳<note n="0784013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">付＝於【甲】</note><note n="0784013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">付【大】，於【甲】</note><app n="0784013"><lem wit="【大】">付</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">於</rdg></app>德美<note n="0784014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔惠謹〕ィ－【甲】</note><note n="0784014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惠謹【大】，〔－〕【校異-甲】</note><app n="0784014"><lem wit="【大】">惠
<lb n="0784a16" ed="T"/>謹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>俗居士趙<note n="0784015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">玖＝梅【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0784015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">玖【大】，梅【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0784015"><lem wit="【大】">玖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】 【丙】">梅</rdg></app></note>三青龍寺曇貞阿闍梨<note place="inline">不傳弟子每有學法者云東塔院有
<lb n="0784a17" ed="T"/>惠果阿闍梨善通教相可<note n="0784016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">於＝相ィ【甲】</note><note n="0784016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，相【校異-甲】</note><app n="0784016"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">相</rdg></app>彼學</note>四保壽寺覺超阿闍梨<note place="inline">傳付契如。惠
