<lb n="0784b10" ed="T"/>故。</note>得金剛界大教。海內流行。枝葉不絕。優
<lb n="0784b11" ed="T"/>曇鉢<note n="0784048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">教＋（海）【乙】</note><note n="0784048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教【大】，教海【乙】</note><app n="0784048"><lem wit="【大】">教</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">教海</rdg></app>。滿字已圓。其有得傳金剛界法者。
<lb n="0784b12" ed="T"/>頓見菩提。入曼荼羅。得授阿闍梨灌頂。如授
<lb n="0784b13" ed="T"/>法輪王位。此大教王名金剛界者。金剛<note n="0784049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0784049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0784049"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0784b14" ed="T"/>堅固義也。以表一切如來法身堅固不壞無
<lb n="0784b15" ed="T"/>生無滅無始無終堅固常<note n="0784050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">存＝住【丙】</note><note n="0784050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">存【大】，住【丙】</note><app n="0784050"><lem wit="【大】">存</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">住</rdg></app>不壞也。界者
<lb n="0784b16" ed="T"/>性也。明一切如來金剛性遍一切有<note n="0784051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">想＝情【甲】</note><note n="0784051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想【大】，情【甲】</note><app n="0784051"><lem wit="【大】">想</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">情</rdg></app>身中
<lb n="0784b17" ed="T"/>本來具足圓滿普賢毘盧遮那大用自<note n="0784052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">性＝在【甲】</note><note n="0784052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">性【大】，在【甲】</note><app n="0784052"><lem wit="【大】">性</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">在</rdg></app>身
<lb n="0784b18" ed="T"/>海性功德。故修瑜伽者。又以大樂普賢金剛
<lb n="0784b19" ed="T"/>慾箭三摩地。破彼無明住地二障種現及二
<lb n="0784b20" ed="T"/>乘種。摧碎無餘。於一念<note n="0784053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頃＝須ィ【甲】</note><note n="0784053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頃【大】，須【校異-甲】</note><app n="0784053"><lem wit="【大】">頃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">須</rdg></app>證大日毘盧遮那
<lb n="0784b21" ed="T"/>位。此<note n="0784054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＝教【甲】</note><note n="0784054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，教【甲】</note><app n="0784054"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">教</rdg></app>又名金剛頂者。如人之身。頂最為
<lb n="0784b22" ed="T"/>勝。此教於一切大乘法中最為尊上。故名金
<lb n="0784b23" ed="T"/>剛頂<note place="inline">梵云<note n="0784055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">縛＝嚩【甲】</note><note n="0784055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縛【大】，嚩【甲】</note><app n="0784055"><lem wit="【大】">縛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">嚩</rdg></app>曰<note n="0784056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚕＝羅【甲】</note><note n="0784056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚕【大】，羅【甲】</note><app n="0784056"><lem wit="【大】">嚕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅</rdg></app>（二合）瑟抳<note n="0784057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（二合）【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784057"><lem wit="【大】">（二合）</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>沙此云金剛頂</note>又是金剛界光
<lb n="0784b24" ed="T"/>明遍照如來現等覺身示現三密五智令一切
<lb n="0784b25" ed="T"/>有情證大圓鏡智成大菩提也。</p>
<lb n="0784b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT51p0784b2601">此經梵本十萬偈。略本四千偈。廣本則有無
<lb n="0784b27" ed="T"/>量百千俱胝那庾多微塵數偈。如金剛頂<note n="0784058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔義〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784058"><lem wit="【大】">義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0784b28" ed="T"/>決中說。南天竺國有大鐵塔。中有金剛界曼
<lb n="0784b29" ed="T"/>荼羅。聖者形像<note n="0784059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鐵鑄＝鑄鐵【甲】</note><note n="0784059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鐵鑄【大】，鑄鐵【甲】</note><app n="0784059"><lem wit="【大】">鐵鑄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鑄鐵</rdg></app>所成。其塔中有梵夾。
<pb n="0784c" xml:id="T51.2081.0784c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0784c01" ed="T"/><note n="0784060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔廣如床〕－【丙】</note><note n="0784060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">廣如床【大】，〔－〕【丙】</note><app n="0784060"><lem wit="【大】">廣如床</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。廣八九尺。高下五六尺盡是金剛
<lb n="0784c02" ed="T"/>界大教王廣梵本經。則知此經廣本有無量
<lb n="0784c03" ed="T"/>百千俱胝那庾多微塵數偈不可以凡心測量
<lb n="0784c04" ed="T"/>如法華化城喻品<note n="0784061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔云〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784061"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>說是法華經如<note n="0784c0401" resp="CBETA" type="add" cb:note_key="T51.0784c04.15">恒【CB】，洹【大】</note><app n="0784c0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA">恒<note type="cf1">T09n0262_p0026c10</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">洹</rdg></app>河沙
<lb n="0784c05" ed="T"/>偈。又藥王本事<note n="0784062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">品＋（云）【丙】</note><note n="0784062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">品【大】，品云【丙】</note><app n="0784062"><lem wit="【大】">品</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">品云</rdg></app>說甄迦羅。頻婆羅阿閦婆
<lb n="0784c06" ed="T"/>等偈。隨根演教廣略不同。即如花嚴經三本。
<lb n="0784c07" ed="T"/>上本有十三千大千世界微塵數偈。四天下
<lb n="0784c08" ed="T"/>微塵數品。中<note n="0784063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔本〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784063"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>有四天下微塵數偈第<note n="0784064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＋（三）【甲】</note><note n="0784064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，三三【甲】</note><app n="0784064"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三三</rdg></app>
<lb n="0784c09" ed="T"/>本十萬偈<note place="inline">即花嚴八十卷經等是<note n="0784065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784065"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>即如金剛頂經梵夾<note n="0784066" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784066"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0784c10" ed="T"/>略本四千偈中本十萬偈。廣本則<note n="0784067" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784067"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>無量百
<lb n="0784c11" ed="T"/>千俱胝那庾多<note n="0784068" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">微＋（塵數）【甲】</note><note n="0784068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">微【大】，微塵數【甲】</note><app n="0784068"><lem wit="【大】">微</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">微塵數</rdg></app>偈又如華嚴經說普<note n="0784069" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賢＝眼【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0784069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賢【大】，眼【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0784069"><lem wit="【大】">賢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【丙】">眼</rdg></app>修
<lb n="0784c12" ed="T"/>多羅。佛剎微塵數修多羅而為眷屬昔姚秦
<lb n="0784c13" ed="T"/>時羅什三藏將此梵<note n="0784070" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔網〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0784070" resp="CBETA" type="mod">網【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0784070"><lem wit="【大】">網</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>經云是大本菩薩戒
<lb n="0784c14" ed="T"/>經。略譯成兩卷。云是此經中淺略行相。又至
<lb n="0784c15" ed="T"/><note n="0784071" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【甲】</note><note n="0784071" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0784071"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>唐開元年中三藏金剛智從南天竺國將
<lb n="0784c16" ed="T"/>得金剛界十萬偈梵夾經。時大海中過大惡
<lb n="0784c17" ed="T"/>風。<note n="0784072" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＋（日）【乙】</note><note n="0784072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三【大】，三日【乙】</note><app n="0784072"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">三日</rdg></app>船中所有寶物舍利功德盡投於海中。
<lb n="0784c18" ed="T"/>時十萬偈梵夾經誤忘亦投於海中。三藏爾
<lb n="0784c19" ed="T"/>時作息災法。遂得風止。故知十萬偈經與此
<lb n="0784c20" ed="T"/>土緣薄故此經王沈沒大海。次<note n="0784073" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔至〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0784073" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0784073"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>太唐天寶
<lb n="0784c21" ed="T"/><note n="0784074" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">九＝元ィ【丙】</note><note n="0784074" resp="CBETA" type="mod">九【大】，元【校異-丙】</note><app n="0784074"><lem wit="【大】">九</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="variantRemark">元</rdg></app>載三藏不空阿闍梨自往五天遍求勝法
<pb n="0785a" xml:id="T51.2081.0785a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0785a01" ed="T"/>行至南天竺國得遇長年普賢阿闍梨。遂再
<lb n="0785a02" ed="T"/>諮求重學金剛界法。將得十萬偈經<note place="inline">故金剛<note n="0785001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">界＋（法）【甲】</note><note n="0785001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">界【大】，界法【甲】</note><app n="0785001"><lem wit="【大】">界</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">界法</rdg></app>前後所學
<lb n="0785a03" ed="T"/>者有少不同</note>所以大興善寺三藏和尚代宗皇帝灌
<lb n="0785a04" ed="T"/>頂之師。每與皇帝講金剛界甚深義味。常在
<lb n="0785a05" ed="T"/>內道場翻譯聖教。門下學徒<note n="0785002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔授〕－【乙】</note><note n="0785002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">授【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0785002"><lem wit="【大】">授</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>持明灌頂者。
<lb n="0785a06" ed="T"/><note n="0785003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">數＋（滿）【甲】</note><note n="0785003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">數【大】，數滿【甲】</note><app n="0785003"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">數滿</rdg></app>盈千萬。昇堂預翻譯者三十<note n="0785004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔餘〕－【丙】</note><note n="0785004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餘【大】，〔－〕【丙】</note><app n="0785004"><lem wit="【大】">餘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>人。入室
<lb n="0785a07" ed="T"/>傳阿闍梨灌頂者。數唯五人<note place="inline">如前<note n="0785005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔文〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">文【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785005"><lem wit="【大】">文</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>已敘</note>金剛界毘
<lb n="0785a08" ed="T"/>盧遮那梵本經百千偈<note place="inline">即十萬偈也</note>說經處有十八
<lb n="0785a09" ed="T"/>會<note place="inline">名目列數次第如十八會指歸說也</note>四大品。一金剛界。二降三
<lb n="0785a10" ed="T"/>世。三遍調伏。四一切義成就<note place="inline">此四種皆金剛界所攝</note>一切
<lb n="0785a11" ed="T"/>法要以四智<note n="0785006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＋（印）ィ【甲】</note><note n="0785006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，印印【校異-甲】</note><app n="0785006"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">印印</rdg></app>攝所謂大印。三摩耶印。法
<lb n="0785a12" ed="T"/>智印。羯磨智印。又一一曼荼羅皆具六曼<note n="0785007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拏＝荼【甲】【丙】＊</note><note n="0785007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拏【大】＊，荼【甲】【丙】＊</note><app n="0785007"><lem wit="【大】">拏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【丙】">荼</rdg></app>
<lb n="0785a13" ed="T"/>羅。一所謂大曼<app type="star" corresp="#0785007"><lem wit="【大】">拏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【丙】">荼</rdg></app>羅。二三昧耶曼荼羅。三
<lb n="0785a14" ed="T"/>法曼荼羅。四羯磨曼荼羅。五四印曼荼羅。六
<lb n="0785a15" ed="T"/>一印曼荼羅。唯降三世曼荼羅具十<note n="0785008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">曼＋（荼羅）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0785008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曼【大】，曼荼羅【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0785008"><lem wit="【大】">曼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】">曼荼羅</rdg></app>。餘皆
<lb n="0785a16" ed="T"/>具六。其經說五部。一佛部<note place="inline">毘盧遮那佛以為部主。四波羅蜜菩薩
<lb n="0785a17" ed="T"/>以為看屬</note>。二金剛部<note place="inline">阿閦佛以為部主四大菩薩以為看屬</note>。三寶部<note place="inline">寶生佛以為部主四
<lb n="0785a18" ed="T"/><note n="0785009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785009"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>菩薩<note n="0785010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＋（大）【甲】</note><note n="0785010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，以大【甲】</note><app n="0785010"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以大</rdg></app>為看屬</note>。四蓮華部<note place="inline">阿彌陀佛以為部主四大菩薩以為看屬</note>。五羯磨
<lb n="0785a19" ed="T"/>部<note place="inline">不空成就佛以為部主四大菩薩以為看屬</note>。內外供養<note n="0785011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔及〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785011"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>四攝<note n="0785012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔成〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785012"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三
<lb n="0785a20" ed="T"/>十七。又說四種法身。一自性身。二受用身。三
<lb n="0785a21" ed="T"/>變化身。四等流身。四種地位。一勝解行地。二
<lb n="0785a22" ed="T"/>普賢行願地。三大普賢地。四普遍照輝地。
<lb n="0785a23" ed="T"/><note n="0785013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（從）＋地【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0785013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">地【大】，從地【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0785013"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】 【丙】">從地</rdg></app>前三賢為勝解行地。從初地至十地為普
<lb n="0785a24" ed="T"/>賢行願地。等覺菩薩為大普賢地。<note n="0785014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛＋（地）【甲】</note><note n="0785014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，佛地【甲】</note><app n="0785014"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">佛地</rdg></app>名普
<lb n="0785a25" ed="T"/>遍照耀地。四種念誦。一聲念誦。二語念誦。
<lb n="0785a26" ed="T"/><note place="inline">亦名金剛念誦謂舌端微動唇齒合</note>三三摩地念誦<note place="inline">謂住定與觀智相應</note>。四勝義
<lb n="0785a27" ed="T"/>念誦<note place="inline">思第一義諦如久之理</note>。四種求願法<note place="inline">謂息災增益降伏敬愛并攝召成五</note>。又
<lb n="0785a28" ed="T"/>瑜伽<note n="0785015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785015"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>中明四種眼<note place="inline">如經說</note>。四種座法<note place="inline">如經說</note>。五種
<lb n="0785a29" ed="T"/>大願<note place="inline">如經說</note>。又一切如來教集瑜伽中說一百二
<pb n="0785b" xml:id="T51.2081.0785b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0785b01" ed="T"/>十種護摩爐。爐中執印標幟各異。所求迅速
<lb n="0785b02" ed="T"/>成辨世出世間果報。諸會<note n="0785016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">浩＝法【甲】</note><note n="0785016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浩【大】，法【甲】</note><app n="0785016"><lem wit="【大】">浩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">法</rdg></app>汗內曼拏羅尊
<lb n="0785b03" ed="T"/>位三十七并賢劫十六大菩薩表賢劫中一千
<lb n="0785b04" ed="T"/>佛。或賢劫千佛皆。在曼荼羅四方。圍繞大
<lb n="0785b05" ed="T"/>曼<note n="0785017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">荼＝拏【甲】＊</note><note n="0785017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">荼【大】＊，拏【甲】＊</note><app n="0785017"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">拏</rdg></app>羅。<note n="0785018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">成＝或ィ【甲】</note><note n="0785018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成【大】，或【校異-甲】</note><app n="0785018"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">或</rdg></app>五十三。并外二十天成七十三。
<lb n="0785b06" ed="T"/>內院地水火風天成<note n="0785019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">七＝三【甲】</note><note n="0785019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七【大】，三【甲】</note><app n="0785019"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三</rdg></app>十七。四角有四忿怒
<lb n="0785b07" ed="T"/>明王<note place="inline">或<note n="0785020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宣＝置【甲】</note><note n="0785020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宣【大】，置【甲】</note><app n="0785020"><lem wit="【大】">宣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">置</rdg></app>標幟形</note>成八十一聖者身。已上總名金
<lb n="0785b08" ed="T"/>剛界大曼<app type="star" corresp="#0785017"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">拏</rdg></app>羅王<note place="inline">內五十三聖者屬灌頂尊餘天等<note n="0785021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔皆〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785021"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>各外金剛<note n="0785022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔部〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">部【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785022"><lem wit="【大】">部</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不入灌
<lb n="0785b09" ed="T"/>頂位</note>金剛界曼荼羅并外金剛部尊身共八十
<lb n="0785b10" ed="T"/>一。皆是金剛界光<note n="0785023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔明〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785023"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>遍照如來之看屬。以表
<lb n="0785b11" ed="T"/>十方三世盡虛空遍法界<note n="0785024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔持〕－【乙】</note><note n="0785024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0785024"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>微塵剎海一切
<lb n="0785b12" ed="T"/>如來身。以為其體是亦十方三世諸佛。般若
<lb n="0785b13" ed="T"/>波羅蜜母悉能出生一切諸佛菩薩金剛薩埵
<lb n="0785b14" ed="T"/>性所成就諸菩薩等。亦能出<note n="0785025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">世＝生【甲】＊</note><note n="0785025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】＊，生【甲】＊</note><app n="0785025"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">生</rdg></app>甚深祕密百
<lb n="0785b15" ed="T"/>千萬億修多羅藏。皆是毘盧遮那如來性海
<lb n="0785b16" ed="T"/>功德亦能出<app type="star" corresp="#0785025"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">生</rdg></app>花藏莊嚴世界海有情世<note n="0785026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">間＝界【丙】＊</note><note n="0785026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">間【大】＊，界【丙】＊</note><app n="0785026"><lem wit="【大】">間</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">界</rdg></app>
<lb n="0785b17" ed="T"/><note n="0785027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔及器世間〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及器世間【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785027"><lem wit="【大】">及器世<app type="star" corresp="#0785026"><lem wit="【大】">間</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">界</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。皆是毘盧遮那如來體性周遍
<lb n="0785b18" ed="T"/>故一身充滿一切剎。故<note n="0785028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔云〕－【甲】【丙】</note><note n="0785028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云【大】，〔－〕【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0785028"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>此教門難逢難遇。
<lb n="0785b19" ed="T"/>故從上傳法者經數百年。外方傳一人。我大
<lb n="0785b20" ed="T"/>興善寺三藏和尚親禮五天。重諮勝法。教流
<lb n="0785b21" ed="T"/>天下。大法盛傳。所以新羅諸國<note n="0785029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＝王【甲】</note><note n="0785029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，王【甲】</note><app n="0785029"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">王</rdg></app>逾數萬。
<lb n="0785b22" ed="T"/>航海忘軀。來趨我唐。至求勝法。故得金剛
<lb n="0785b23" ed="T"/><note n="0785030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">界＋（法）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0785030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">界【大】，界法【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0785030"><lem wit="【大】">界</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】">界法</rdg></app>累代相承每年有勅。於大興善寺及青龍
<lb n="0785b24" ed="T"/>寺保壽興唐崇福醲<note n="0785031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">泉＋（等）ィ【甲】</note><note n="0785031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泉【大】，泉等【校異-甲】</note><app n="0785031"><lem wit="【大】">泉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">泉等</rdg></app><note n="0785032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔寺〕－【甲】</note><note n="0785032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寺【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0785032"><lem wit="【大】">寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。大開灌頂。傳法
<lb n="0785b25" ed="T"/>度人。是皆我大興善寺三藏和尚傳法之孫
<lb n="0785b26" ed="T"/><note n="0785033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔資也〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0785033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">資也【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0785033"><lem wit="【大】">資也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】 【乙】 【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>弘教枝葉遞相傳持。永<note n="0785034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">久＝永【甲】</note><note n="0785034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">久【大】，永【甲】</note><app n="0785034"><lem wit="【大】">久</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">永</rdg></app>無盡。苾芻
<lb n="0785b27" ed="T"/>海雲<note n="0785035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頃＝須【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0785035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頃【大】，須【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0785035"><lem wit="【大】">頃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】 【丙】">須</rdg></app>因餘暇。時屬仲秋之月。謹依本教略
<lb n="0785b28" ed="T"/>集金剛界大教王師資相承傳法次第。從普
<lb n="0785b29" ed="T"/>賢金剛薩埵至今所傳繼于八葉。</p>
<pb n="0785c" xml:id="T51.2081.0785c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0785c01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT51p0785c0101">敬禮金剛界自在。普賢薩埵持明王。</p>
<lb n="0785c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT51p0785c0201">迴<note n="0785036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝斯【甲】</note><note n="0785036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此【大】，斯【甲】</note><app n="0785036"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">斯</rdg></app>讚演施群生。普願同生<note n="0785037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">華藏＝藏花【甲】</note><note n="0785037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">華藏【大】，藏花【甲】</note><app n="0785037"><lem wit="【大】">華藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">藏花</rdg></app>界。</p>
<lb n="0785c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT51p0785c0301">巨唐大和八年歲在甲寅仲秋月二十日</p>
<lb n="0785c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT51p0785c0401" style="margin-left:5em">淨住寺梵字傳教沙門海雲集</p></cb:div>
